#for stripe setup and paymnet-service
if want to start the paymnet service you have download stripe for windows, for mac refer this link :https://docs.stripe.com/stripe-cli?install-method=windows

after download extract put the env variables
then open cmd run stripe login do the authentication using our common Foodrush48 email
then run the below command to start the stripe cli and forward the webhook to our payment service
stripe listen --forward-to localhost:9400/api/pay/webhook
sometime you will come new webhook secret, so copy that and put in the env file as STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET

dont run this
stripe trigger checkout.session.completed


#for whatsapp message to work we have to register our number in meta cloude api.untill that no message other than to my number will be sent.
#implemented the whatsapp message for user registration. 
#template created for order_placed, order_dellivered_dr, account_created, tenmapltes are created in the meta cloude api. so you just have to use the template name(refere postman)
#refere the postman to get the payload, and refere the code in user-service -> src -> services> user.service.js to see how to send the message.